txt.en: Cargaraf, Morgaraf's brother, is possessed of the powers of fire.
Defeat the Lieutenant of Dol Guldur
Morgaraf, Cargaraf's sister, is possessed of the powers of shadow.
The Lieutenant of Dol Guldur is the Steward of Barad Guldur, and leader of Sauron's forces in Southern Mirkwood.
Even the sorcerer Gorothúl must bow to the power of the Lieutenant of Dol Guldur and his wraith-minions.
Dúrchest is the Captain of the Guard for Barad Guldur.
